Speaker 2: I agree. It's all about understanding people at the end of the day, isn't it?

Speaker 1: Couldn't have said it better myself. Anyway, it was nice catching up. We should do this more often.

Speaker 2: Definitely! It's always nice to have a chat with a neighbor. Have a good day!

Speaker 1: You too, take care!
